This paper discusses the validation of network paths for secure Internet architecture, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and computer networks (cs.NI). It also touches upon the efficiency and privacy aspects, which could be related to systems and control (cs.SI), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), and software engineering (cs.SE).
